<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>작품 상세 - SKKU Faculty Art Gallery</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <h1>SKKU Faculty Art Gallery</h1>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="/exhibition">전시회</a></li>
                <li><a href="/notice">공지사항</a></li>
                <li><a href="/user/login">로그인</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="artwork-detail">
        <div class="artwork-header">
            <div class="artwork-info">
                <h2>봄의 풍경</h2>
                <p class="artist">김예술</p>
                <p class="category">회화</p>
                <p class="date">2024.02</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="artwork-content">
            <div class="artwork-image">
                <img src="/images/artworks/painting1.jpg" alt="봄의 풍경">
            </div>
            <div class="artwork-description">
                <h3>작품 설명</h3>
                <p>봄의 따스한 햇살과 꽃이 피어나는 순간을 담은 수채화 작품입니다. 자연의 생동감과 계절의 변화를 표현하고자 했습니다.</p>
                
                <div class="artwork-details">
                    <h4>작품 정보</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>제작 연도:</strong> 2024</li>
                        <li><strong>재료:</strong> 수채화, 아쿼렐 용지</li>
                        <li><strong>크기:</strong> 297mm x 420mm</li>
                        <li><strong>소속:</strong> 성균관대학교 미술동아리</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="related-works">
            <h3>관련 작품</h3>
            <div class="exhibition-grid">
                <article class="exhibition-card">
                    <a href="/exhibition/4">
                        <img src="/images/artworks/painting2.jpg" alt="다른 수채화 작품">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>여름 정원</h4>
                            <p class="artist">김예술</p>
                            <p class="category">회화</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
                <article class="exhibition-card">
                    <a href="/exhibition/5">
                        <img src="/images/artworks/painting3.jpg" alt="또 다른 수채화 작품">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>가을 산책</h4>
                            <p class="artist">김예술</p>
                            <p class="category">회화</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 SKKU Faculty Art Gallery. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 